channel.title: Easy to edit source supports silabsoft?
channel.description:
hey im looking for a silabsoft compatible source which is easy to edit and DOES what you tell it to. I have too many servers that have problems with things such as the ::commands command which do not let you edit the list and other items. so y' know
im looking for one that preferably allready has silabsoft working. i do not want someone else work just a working source with silab installed would you say?
this is because i have tried it and i can spawn the items on the floor but when i pickup they turn into woopsies and i cant use ::pickup to get them either.
anybody know?
